hannels</span></div></a></li><li class="megaMenuItem"><a class="megaMenuItemLink" href="/ambassadors/"><div class="megaMenuItemContent"><span class="megaMenuItemLabel">Ambassador Program</span><span class="megaMenuItemDescription">Meet Cardano Ambassadors</span></div></a></li></ul></div><div class="megaMenuColumn"><div class="megaMenuColumnTitle"><img src="/img/icons/comments-solid.svg" alt="" class="megaMenuColumnIcon" aria-hidden="true">Engage</div><ul class="megaMenuColumnList"><li class="megaMenuItem"><a class="megaMenuItemLink" href="/events/"><div class="megaMenuItemContent"><span class="megaMenuItemLabel">Cardano Events</span><span class="megaMenuItemDescription">Join Cardano community events</span></div></a></li><li class="megaMenuItem"><a href="https://forum.cardano.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="megaMenuItemLink"><div class="megaMenuItemContent"><span class="megaMenuItemLabel">Cardano Forum</span><span class="megaMenuItemDescription">Structured long-format discussions</span></div></a></li><li class="megaMenuItem"><a class="megaMenuItemLink" href="/docs/get-involved/"><div class="megaMenuItemContent"><span class="megaMenuItemLabel">Get involved in cardano.org</span><span class="megaMenuItemDescription">If you&#x27;d like to participate, this will get you started</span></div></a></li></ul></div><div class="megaMenuColumn"><div class="megaMenuColumnTitle"><img src="/img/icons/users-solid.svg" alt="" class="megaMenuColumnIcon" aria-hidden="true">Governance</div><ul class="megaMenuColumnList"><li class="megaMenuItem"><a class="megaMenuItemLink" href="/governance/"><div class="megaMenuItemContent"><span class="megaMenuItemLabel">Participate in governance</span><span class="megaMenuItemDescription">Shape Cardano&#x27;s future</span></div></a></li><li class="megaMenuItem"><a class="megaMenuItemLink" href="/apps/?tags=governance"><div class="megaMenuItemContent"><span class="megaMenuItemLabel">Governance Tools</span><span class="megaMenuItemDescription">Tools for transparent, community-driven decisions</span></div></a></li><li class="megaMenuItem"><a class="megaMenuItemLink" href="/constitution/"><div class="megaMenuItemContent"><span class="megaMenuItemLabel">Cardano Constitution</span><span class="megaMenuItemDescription">Learn about governance</span></div></a></li></ul></div></div></div></li><li class="navbar__item navbar__item--mega" data-column-count="2"><button class="navbar__link megaMenuTrigger" type="button">Build</button><div class="megaMenuPanel"><div class="megaMenuInner"><div class="megaMenuColumn"><div class="megaMenuColumnTitle"><img src="/img/icons/code-solid.svg" alt="" class="megaMenuColumnIcon" aria-hidden="true">Get started</div><ul class="megaMenuColumnList"><li class="megaMenuItem"><a class="megaMenuItemLink" href="/developers/"><div class="megaMenuItemContent"><span class="megaMenuItemLabel">Start building on Cardano</span><span class="megaMenuItemDescription">Developer resources and tooling</span></div></a></li><li class="megaMenuItem"><a class="megaMenuItemLink" href="/exchanges/"><div class="megaMenuItemContent"><span class="megaMenuItemLabel">Integrate Cardano</span><span class="megaMenuItemDescription">Exchange and integration guides</span></div></a></li></ul></div><div class="megaMenuColumn"><div class="megaMenuColumnTitle"><img src="/img/icons/wrench-solid.svg" alt="" class="megaMenuColumnIcon" aria-hidden="true">Tools</div><ul class="megaMenuColumnList"><li class="megaMenuItem"><a href="https://developers.cardano.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="megaMenuItemLink"><div class="megaMenuItemContent"><span class="megaMenuItemLabel">Developer Portal</span><span class="megaMenuItemDescription">Cardano developer portal and docs</span></div></a></li><li class="megaMenuItem"><a href="https://developers.cardano.org/tools" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="megaMenuItemLink"><div class="megaMenuItemContent"><span class="megaMenuItemLabel">Builder Too